We also fight for people and small businesses who have lost money as a result of a breach of contract or other contract dispute. Our guiding principle is that each client is an individual with specific needs and goals who deserves personalized attention to his or her case. We strive to provide outstanding individualized client service and fight aggressively to obtain for our clients every dollar that they deserve. This approach, together with our experience in auto accident litigation, has allowed us to obtain six and seven-figure settl ements and verdicts for traffic accident victims. If you have been injured in an auto accident or because of someone else’s negligence, or if you have lost money as a result of a contract dispute, please know that we will put our knowledge, experience and passion to work for you until you have received just compensation.

Nuestra práctica de derecho está basada en el principio que cada cliente es un individuo con necesidades y metas únicas que merece un abogado que trate su caso con la misma eficacia y pasión como si fuera su propio caso. El abogado Ernesto trabaja duro para darle a sus clientes un servicio individual y profesional, y lucha agresivamente con las compañías de seguro para que sus clientes reciban todo el dinero que se me recen.
